<br>
I have never met Graffe in game, as we don't play on the same server.  But I think often that this site is what keeps me going.<br>
<br>
So thank you Graffe, and all the regular contributors, for being our &quot;voice.&quot;  Even now as the class is perhaps at a great crossroads -  many of us may be laying down our burdens - I just want to say &quot;thanks.&quot;<br>
